------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This app fetches images from the imgur gallery using the imgur api
and displays them on a web-page using react and node.

The request is done at the start, so your should see images after a few seconds load on the right hand side.

Instructions to run are below.

Thanks,

Jonathan

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To start the server (http://localhost:1234): |
--------------------------------------------
1. node ./server/index.js
--------------------------------------------
To start the client (http://localhost:3000): |
--------------------------------------------
1. *open a new tab*
2. cd client
3. npm start
--------------------------------------------
